summary: This is an email chain forwarding a premises search warrant bundle related to a 156-acre property. The correspondence discusses technical issues with accessing the document and references specific paragraphs (15 and 3) that define the subject premises.

events.title: Forwarding of Premises Search Warrant Bundle

keyFacts: The document references a premises search warrant bundle for a 156-acre property.

Paragraph 15 and Paragraph 3 of the search warrant are specifically mentioned as defining the subject premises.
